Class PacketCreateClientSidePlayer

java.lang.Object
necesse.engine.network.Packet
com.jubiman.customdatalib.client.PacketCreateClientSidePlayer
public class PacketCreateClientSidePlayer extends necesse.engine.network.Packet
Packet sent from the server to the client to create a client-side player. Sent only once after client has connected.
